2. **LIKE wildcard injection** — search terms containing `%` or `_` acted as SQL wildcards; `%` matched every listing
3. **Unbounded mark-all-read** — bulk UPDATE with no limit could lock SQLite WAL; bounded to 1000 rows
4. **Unbounded reading history** — no LIMIT on query; added LIMIT 200
5. **ORDER BY hardening** — replaced if/else with explicit allowlist map
6. **Transporter cache stale** — nodemailer transporter never rebuilt when SMTP env vars changed; added config hash invalidation

